

Installation
------------

  Installing this program, from source, should be as simple as running:

             make install

  To remove, please run:

             make uninstall


Requirements
------------

  The requirements of this program are minimal and can be installed
 by:

   apt-get update
   apt-get install rpm alien wget



Steve
